                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-17-off100 t18000528-17-cd101"></join>, a cheese, value 16s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000528-17-victim228" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Winkworth
