                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-17-defend226 t18000528-17-punish105"></join>
               Confined one month in Newgate, and delivered to his serjeant
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
